Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  愛的Baiser
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}有什麼好感動的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不奇怪
